# Tailwind v4

Entry: `@import "tailwindcss"` + `@config` in `app/globals.css` · tokens in `tailwind.config.ts`.

## Single sources

| Concern | Path |
|---------|------|
| Repeated class strings | `lib/tailwind.ts` (`TW_*`) — see also `16-dry.mdc` |
| Brand, shadows, gradients | `tailwind.config.ts` |
| Rich text | `rich-text` classes in `globals.css` — **not** `prose-*` |
| PT wrapper component | `components/content/RichTextBody.tsx` |
| Scroll/reveal utilities | `@utility` in globals; Reveal `.rv-*` |

## Do
- Utilities in `className` only — no CSS-in-JS
- Import `TW_EYEBROW`, `TW_SECTION_TITLE`, `TW_GOLD_CTA`, etc. before duplicating
- `shrink-0` not `flex-shrink-0` · slash opacity `bg-dq-500/20`
- Theme shadows: `shadow-gold-*`, `shadow-nav`, `shadow-gold-subtle`
- RTL spacing → `03-rtl-urdu.mdc` (logical props)

## Don't
- `@tailwindcss/typography` or `prose-*`
- Inline `style={{}}` for colors/gradients/shadows  
  OK: `--hero-delay`, LCP blur, `--nav-indent` CSS vars
- Raw hex for brand UI · duplicate arbitrary rgba shadows
- `@apply` except base/rich-text in `globals.css`

## Brand exceptions
PayPal (`TW_PAYPAL_CTA`), WhatsApp (`TW_WHATSAPP_FLOAT`) only.

